data.description: Back on the market! (No fault of the Seller) Cozy Florida cottage with old-charm, tucked in on a cul-de-sac! Big enough for the whole family, nestled in quaint neighborhood, within walking distance to Rhodes Elementary school. Extra large main bedroom, with two ceiling fans and sliding glass door. (Carpet will be replaced in this room.) Enjoy the natural sunlight that dazzles throughout this home and watch the world go by from the large front windows in the Library! Knotty Pine, wood-paneled walls, accent the first living area giving the room a groovy retro vibe! Large kitchen with gas range! Large second living area/dining area. Nice sized second & third bedrooms. Charming details in the home; Pocket door and barn style door on bathrooms! Nice size laundry/mud room! Hardwood floors & ceramic tile throughout. Metal roof, and large deck, with main bedroom access, overlooking large, partially fenced in, backyard. This home has so much potential to be your old-Florida dream home! Ready to be shown!
